00:45:04,220 --> 00:45:05,620
Untuk berubah.

557
00:45:05,722 --> 00:45:08,289
Children of the Forest menemukanku.

558
00:45:08,391 --> 00:45:11,592
Menghentikan sihir White Walker.

559
00:45:11,695 --> 00:45:12,994
Caranya ?

560
00:45:13,096 --> 00:45:15,396
Sama seperti saat mereka
menciptakan White Walker.

561
00:45:15,498 --> 00:45:16,831
Kau sudah melihatnya sendiri.

562
00:45:18,635 --> 00:45:20,635
Dragonglass.

